    <item>
      <title>习近平向特朗普伸出橄榄枝 警告“红线”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-11-18/xi-offers-olive-branch-to-trump-warning-on-red-lines-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国领导人习近平告诉美国总统乔·拜登，他已准备好与唐纳德·特朗普合作，改善世界两大经济体之间的关系。彭博新闻社执行编辑刘约翰报道了《彭博：亚洲贸易》。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-11-18/xi-offers-olive-branch-to-trump-warning-on-red-lines-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 18 Nov 2024 02:11:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>香港交易所陈茂波：建立互联互通机制还有很长的“待办事项”清单</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-11-18/hkex-s-chan-long-to-do-list-on-building-connect-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[香港交易所运营商香港交易所首席执行官 Bonnie Chan 表示，人们对 IPO 互联互通计划非常感兴趣。她与 Stephen Engle 讨论了扩大交易所互联互通计划的进展。她在纪念沪港通 10 周年活动间隙接受了“彭博社：亚洲交易”节目的采访。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-11-18/hkex-s-chan-long-to-do-list-on-building-connect-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 18 Nov 2024 01:22:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>利率前景不断变化，黄金在周度大幅下跌后反弹</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-18/gold-rebounds-after-deep-weekly-loss-with-rate-outlook-in-flux</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于美元走软且考虑到唐纳德·特朗普明年重返白宫，交易员权衡美联储降息前景，金价在遭遇 2021 年以来最大单周跌幅后上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-18/gold-rebounds-after-deep-weekly-loss-with-rate-outlook-in-flux</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 18 Nov 2024 01:19:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>比特币价格创美国大选以来最大跌幅，跌至近 90,000 美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-18/bitcoin-btc-trades-near-90-000-after-largest-drop-since-us-election</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于交易员评估当选总统唐纳德·特朗普的政策议程的潜在影响，全球市场出现谨慎情绪，比特币上周末出现自美国大选以来的最大两日跌幅。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-18/bitcoin-btc-trades-near-90-000-after-largest-drop-since-us-election</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 18 Nov 2024 01:09:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>错失人工智能热潮后，三星股价因 70 亿美元回购而上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-18/samsung-jumps-as-surprise-7-billion-buyback-welcomed-by-market</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国最大的公司三星电子公司意外宣布计划在未来一年回购约 10 万亿韩元（72 亿美元）自有股票，随后其股价飙升。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-18/samsung-jumps-as-surprise-7-billion-buyback-welcomed-by-market</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 18 Nov 2024 00:08:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
