      <title>受供应过剩担忧和中国需求前景影响，油价本周维持跌势</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-17/oil-holds-weekly-loss-on-glut-concerns-china-s-demand-outlook</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于对供应充足以及全球最大原油进口国中国的需求前景的担忧，油价本周持续下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-17/oil-holds-weekly-loss-on-glut-concerns-china-s-demand-outlook</guid>
