    <item>
      <title>关税风险加剧市场紧张情绪 韩元或面临更大压力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-17/korean-won-set-to-fall-further-as-tariff-risk-adds-to-jitters</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩元是今年亚洲表现第二差的货币，由于唐纳德·特朗普的关税威胁给这个依赖出口的国家的经济前景蒙上阴影，韩元似乎将进一步贬值。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-17/korean-won-set-to-fall-further-as-tariff-risk-adds-to-jitters</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 17 Nov 2024 23:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>港股通开通十周年 投资者关注 IPO 渠道</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-17/investors-eye-ipo-access-as-hong-kong-stock-link-turns-10</link>
      <description><![CDATA[十年前，中国通过与香港的贸易联系向广大国际投资者开放了国内交易所，如今投资者渴望获得更深层次的准入。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-17/investors-eye-ipo-access-as-hong-kong-stock-link-turns-10</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 17 Nov 2024 23:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
